{"tid":1221801,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"因為去左野餐比老細秋後算帳既入一入黎","createTime":"2019-06-14T09:47:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T18:08:43.000Z","uid":27797,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"135c243129908ec341941bd4cf263f50634295d2","tid":1221801,"uid":27797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:47:05.000Z","msg":"見到身邊已經有唔同人因為去野餐比老細警告甚至炒魷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家如果面對呢個情況，第一時間緊係諗上勞工處告鳩個仆街老細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係有兩個事實大家要清楚：<br />\n第一，香港僱傭條例基本上係廢既，正常黎講老細只要比足通知你再炒，除非係你放緊產假、工傷或者有薪病假（可能要病夠四日先有）期間，咁樣先叫違法。仲有一個可能性，就係因為你<strong>參加工會活動</strong>而炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二，眾所周知勞工處都係廢既，唔講佢本身就係政府一部份，甚至有情況係明明有得追，勞工處職員都可以同你講無得追。因為耍走左你佢就少樣野做，公務員心態就係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以，如果真係比老細秋後算帳既，我建議你地唔好第一時間就去搵勞工處，而係應該搵左工會先。因為勞資糾紛問題，工會一定最有經驗同資格幫手，就算上到法庭，都只係得工會有權代表你屌鳩個老細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n叫你搵工會，咁緊係唔係叫你搵工聯會啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />職工盟其實已經出左post，叫人如果被老闆搞可以聯絡佢地，而且職工盟前幾日都有叫人唔好番工，如果大家係因為響應工會活動而比老細炒，工會可能都有方法幫到你既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n職工盟post：<br />\n6月12日，有唔少打工仔都響應停工/罷工，參加反送中集會。但我哋收到有打工仔嘅消息，竟然因此被腦細照肺盤問。所以，我哋而家收集緊秋後算帳嘅公司名單，呼籲市民抵制下列公司，並作出跟進行動。如果各位打工仔有上述經歷，請提供資料到以下google form，我哋會聯絡你哋！如有任何疑問，請致電2770 8668查詢。<br />\n*資料經當時人提供證據核實。<br />\n*當事人的資料一概保密。<br />\n<br />\n香港職工會聯盟<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2X4kJsf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2X4kJsf&d=%2Bo9ZPOFl8lx%2FL2stOySvpAWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=86d69740\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2X4kJsf</a>"},{"pid":"6e687a85680e2d5fd97df567c3b887b7f6d0f2fa","tid":1221801,"uid":231015,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:48:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>民陣 6.16&nbsp;反修訂《逃犯條例》遊行</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">日期：2019年6月16日（日）<br />\n時間：下午2時30分集合、3時正起步<br />\n集合地點：維園草地 <br />\n終點：金鐘政府總部</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>大家一定要到！！！</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"9237cb888947553d357df429f6ea6cfc7301d990","tid":1221801,"uid":27797,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:59:16.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"d7662d512b3da04180c7f6df45d1cb54a2f84304","tid":1221801,"uid":27797,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T10:06:07.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"73664c3a1714f350af565c9e292e28f8bac0b0ef","tid":1221801,"uid":27797,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T10:10:52.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"27eba1fb6c8c6e66bb474ca41eae2a6325b5deec","tid":1221801,"uid":27797,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T10:18:49.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"4525ebded2cbfe19b34e4d1da8ebd24fde30a158","tid":1221801,"uid":27797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T10:31:28.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"c5eeb9d147d58560d2c609294526ed2d12d4b142","tid":1221801,"uid":27797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T10:52:24.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"9b250b8fa6e392188cbafd2ea99ab7ec5c04668c","tid":1221801,"uid":27266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T11:35:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"14b641ea087e2332759235318b88f59ed9395b27","tid":1221801,"uid":27797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T14:00:15.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"15cfd831fc0255d026f600aa0766c8204796715b","tid":1221801,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:03:35.000Z","msg":"全部告勞工署先啦."},{"pid":"9ff9b78351a0ddfaf417a7df2e68528b34e70adf","tid":1221801,"uid":140538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:06:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bf9257cc84228415313c11e32f7fff491c1f1087","tid":1221801,"uid":27797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:04:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cbac24d82aae640d08a44c43fdea1aacd860b8be","tid":1221801,"uid":27797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T18:08:43.000Z","msg":"推"}]}